#폼태그 만들기

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content=""width=device-width, initial-scale="1.0">
	<link rel="icon" jref="../../images/logo.png"/>
	<title>폼 알아보기</title>
</head>
<body>
    <form method="post"> **method="post" 얘가 빠져야 제출을 눌렀을 때 page not found가 안 뜸** **get방식은 아이디 비번이 노출돼서 post로 씀-보안이슈**
        아이디: <input type="text" name="txt" required placeholder="글 작성해주세요"/> 
        **name=txt가 정의가 되어있어야 함. 얜 input이 갖고 있는 변수를 뜻함** 
        **required가 있어야 빈칸 상태에서 제출 할 때 입력하라는 안내문이 뜸"**
        <!-- <input type="submit" /> -->
         <button type="submit">제출</button>
         **input submit이나 button type 둘 중 하나만 쓰기**
    </form>
</body>
</html>

#코드
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content=""width=device-width, initial-scale="1.0">
	<link rel="icon" jref="../../images/logo.png"/>
	<title>폼 알아보기</title>
</head>
<body>
    <form>
        아이디: <input type="text" name="txt" required placeholder="글 작성해주세요"/>
        <!-- <input type="submit" /> -->
         <button type="submit">제출</button>
    </form>
</body>
</html>

#코드
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta anme="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
        <title>폼태그</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <form>
            <input type="text" name="txt" required placeholder="글 작성해 주세요">
            <button type="submit">제출</button>
        </form>
    </body>
</html>
